The file to run our project is main.py
The 4 modes for running the main file are:

    To run the baseline model on the dev set
    python main.py

    To run the baseline model on the test set and write answers.csv
    python main.py -bt

    To run the enhanced model on the dev set
    python main.py -e

    To run the enhanced model on the test set and write answers.csv
    python main.py -t

********************
Also included is a file called basic_classifier_test.py that was used for tuning the basic query classifier
this can be run by just calling it so :
    python basic_classifier_test.py